"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"No, it doesn’t deplete it quicker because harnessing the sun’s energy is passive, not active, meaning we can only extract what it offers, rather than controlling what we extract. What changes is the form that energy takes, depending how we use it.\\n\\nAgreed. Definitely needs to be a regulated industry. Maybe an introduction of a sunlight harvesting tax might reduce the rate at which this precious commodity is being thieved.\\n\\nLets assume he does indeed exist our god: who created him? if he was not created... how did he appear? if he was always there then why did our universe only come to exist 13.5b years ago? Before that? Else he was bored big time or already created universes. We are unimportant...\\n\\nThis universe is manifested inside of God, who is pure consciousness. The universe did not begin 13.5b years ago, it is only the last day of Brahma that started then, according to the Vedas. Innumerable universes are created, maintainted and dissolved. The Vedas explain it all.\\n\\nThank you. Lol. It is only man who told you the universe was created 13.5B years ago and truth is... Your experts and their machines have no clue.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/3AR9YgC5UiLfk_ybgtjYl.jpg?height=400&width=400)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1638371438,\"title\":\"Doesn’t even need maintenance – just works!\"},\"digest\":\"QxCFAfDt0t9HluiGBZd2atyqLppX6ViSSzq0Bl6wJ_k\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x742cFe2a1fb49AE444C91b696C771A7b2F65E9f4\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"WlYrgMxLpF0rEqpOdmn1cinrQBGjD8rN0y2MLQrDyb8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ZmEuPTgy0X8LSo7mLOCg9lgpp6YMwjBcf1UdyVs3gm8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"QOXI2nHFVOV69XYJiWE8CcAXkb3IkYIjnW9SYdqIRfcyTRCuFPu07dZFic0_ZyQnc4JbqhtqS49Zm1cJUUhpBg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xf6d9d3880a73be40bb572e66c4315e40db88c8a0c7bdf5823cc6433b4a7d81a62a130da462fad53b85c4c3779765b1e042061664dbac